title: "Kohitar the Xenolith"
editor: 
  markdown: 
    wrap: sentence
---

Kohitar (Mountain of Darkness) the Xenolith is one of the three lieutenants of Dr. Petra Pufferfish.
They are a RADIOACTIVE GEM TALOS covered in an OBSIDIAN LAVA TALOS via a symbiotic relationship.

Their gem core is the [Koh-i-Noor](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Koh-i-Noor), the largest diamond in the world, it was in the Crown of the regent of the UK.

Is able to build incredibly energy dense batteries with diamond battery technology (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diamond_battery).

Wants nothing more than to erupt volcanoes.